INSTALLATION INSTRUCTIONS

User installation:

1 - Extract the archive to ~/.kde/share/apps/desktoptheme (Remove old directory if it exists) 
2 - Enable the theme in systemsettings or by edit the plasmarc file located in
    ~/.kde/share/config/plasmarc or
    ~/.kde4/share/config/plasmarc
    and change
    [Theme]
    name=Default with name=Volatile
3 - Log out and in again if changes hasnt occured